short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Convert current page in pdf format

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With the Bikub Save as Pdf chrome extension, you can download any web page as a pdf document.

You just need to install the plugin.

Then just click on the "save as pdf" button when you want to transform the content of the site into pdf.
